answers.body_markdown:
From what I can see your call to setData is in onCreateView.
If the view is only created once then it will only be called once.

This will happen if you move on to another activity and then return to this one.
Since the activity was not destroyed, it will not be recreated and it will use the one that already exists.

You need to update the data whenever you show the fragment.
For this use onResume in the fragment.

    @Override
    public void onResume(){
        super.onResume();
            
        setData();
    }

