I came across same problem few days back.
In my case, the reason was less buffer sizes in Kubernetes configuration file.
Try increasing buffer sizes to following -

```
http{
...
proxy_buffer_size   128k;
proxy_buffers   4 256k;
proxy_busy_buffers_size   256k;
large_client_header_buffers 4 16k;
...
}
```

For more detailed answer, please refer following link - 

https://medium.com/@mshanak/solve-nginx-error-signin-oidc-502-bad-gateway-dotnet-core-and-identity-serve-bc27920b42d5

Hope this resolves your issue!

